#MensHealthWeek #BowelCancer -polyps are more common as we get older & most are NOT pre-cancerous. One type can become cancerous, an Adenoma
#MensHealthWeek #BowelCancer - the important is that if diagnosed early bowel cancer can be treated successfully in over 90% of cases.
